  "detailed_description": "Moonlight Mayhem is a 4-15 player multiplayer horror game. The objective is to find and kill the werewolves infiltrated among the players. These are designated at the start of the game and their goal is to eliminate the other players without being noticed. Many items are available throughout the map to spice up the game.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2475330/extras/159f35c6727fcea44650203a15ae20ca.webp?t=1699739386\" width=230 height=58 /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2475330/extras/a102ad6bdc32d59e67ae0e3da5fee4ce.poster.avif?t=1699739386\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2475330/extras/a102ad6bdc32d59e67ae0e3da5fee4ce.webm?t=1699739386\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2475330/extras/a102ad6bdc32d59e67ae0e3da5fee4ce.mp4?t=1699739386\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2475330/extras/1c2c0e8b72f7e6f8c2c27b36f145d27e.webp?t=1699739386\" width=230 height=58 /></span><br><strong>Play with your friends from 4 to 15 players.</strong><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2475330/extras/422038315e006b4e40570cff3d5c19c9.poster.avif?t=1699739386\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2475330/extras/422038315e006b4e40570cff3d5c19c9.webm?t=1699739386\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2475330/extras/422038315e006b4e40570cff3d5c19c9.mp4?t=1699739386\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2475330/extras/290794317994c0c4627f9117e8754b49.webp?t=1699739386\" width=230 height=58 /></span><br><strong>Play as the enemy side and try to eliminate everyone.</strong><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2475330/extras/14e03b16b40f088f42cc6ec5c5f5be2b.poster.avif?t=1699739386\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2475330/extras/14e03b16b40f088f42cc6ec5c5f5be2b.webm?t=1699739386\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2475330/extras/14e03b16b40f088f42cc6ec5c5f5be2b.mp4?t=1699739386\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2475330/extras/dc988621a39e4b499cd5341483d933be.webp?t=1699739386\" width=230 height=58 /></span><br><strong>Customize your character.</strong><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2475330/extras/dd0e8f1b68f9e91695928c2811c3926d.poster.avif?t=1699739386\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2475330/extras/dd0e8f1b68f9e91695928c2811c3926d.webm?t=1699739386\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2475330/extras/dd0e8f1b68f9e91695928c2811c3926d.mp4?t=1699739386\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>",
